  "title": "Mobile Crane Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Newcomer Bonus</li>\n  <li>5.5 days’ work week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure crane is in good working condition before operation; always be alert and ensure safe operation at work</li>\n  <li>To be fully aware of related WSH safety regulations and house rules</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular maintenance and cleaning/disinfecting of crane’s cabin</li>\n  <li>Report any malfunction, wear and tear of crane</li>\n  <li>Any other responsibilities as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Singapore Class 5 Driving license is a must</li>\n  <li>Must be a registered Mobile Crane Operator with MOM</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Willing to work on weekends and Public Holidays, night shift works, when required</li>\n</ul>",
